In 2026, Pi 5 homelabs are mainstream. Popular additions: Portainer (containers), Ollama (local AI), Pi-hole (ad blocking), Uptime Kuma (monitoring), Cloudflared (tunneling). NVMe + ARM64 Docker makes Pi 5 viable for always-on services. Consider adding Ollama for local LLM inference as future beestgraph enhancement.

